      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the subframe has been reinforced\u2014critical preventative measures for this chassis. It retains a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox with short-throw precision. The suspension features refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers, ensuring the 50/50 weight distribution translates to exceptional turn-in and lateral grip. While the exterior shows minor patina consistent with a driver's car, the mechanical vitals\u2014including compression across all cylinders and cooling system integrity\u2014are top-tier. A visceral, analog driving experience for the true purist.",
