      "description": "Offering a meticulously maintained daily driver that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior is finished in a timeless metallic silver that retains a high-gloss luster; however, in the interest of full disclosure, there are a few minor stone chips on the leading edge of the hood and a small, shallow scuff on the lower rear bumper from city parking. The body panels are straight with no dings or dents. Inside, the charcoal leather interior remains in excellent shape, showing only light softening and minor creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, with no cracks or punctures. All interior electronics, including the navigation system, heated seats, and dual-zone climate control, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is robust. It has been serviced at regular intervals with high-quality synthetic fluids, and the engine runs quietly with a smooth, responsive transmission. The tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining, and the brakes were serviced less than 3,000 miles ago. This vehicle has been smoke-free and garage-kept, providing a clean, dependable option for its next owner.",
